<!DOCTYPE html>
<html class="h-full bg-gray-900">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no">

    <title>{% block title %}Welcome!{% endblock %}</title>

    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="{{ asset('img/favicon.png') }}" />

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="{{ asset('css/main.css') }}">

    {# Run `composer require symfony/webpack-encore-bundle` to start using Symfony UX #}
    {% block stylesheets %}
        {{ encore_entry_link_tags('app') }}
    {% endblock %}

    {% block javascripts %}
        {{ encore_entry_script_tags('app') }}
    {% endblock %}
</head>
<body class="antialiased h-full">

{% if error %}
    <div>{{ error.messageKey|trans(error.messageData, 'security') }}</div>
{% endif %}


<div class="flex min-h-full flex-col justify-center px-6 py-12 lg:px-8">
    <div class="sm:mx-auto sm:w-full sm:max-w-sm">
        <img class="h-8 w-auto mx-auto" src="{{ asset('img/logo.svg') }}" alt="Woodstock">
        <h2 class="mt-10 text-center text-2xl font-bold leading-9 tracking-tight text-white">Se connecter à Woodstock</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-10 sm:mx-auto sm:w-full sm:max-w-sm">
        <form class="space-y-6" action="{{ path('app_login') }}" method="post">
            <div>
                <label for="email" class="block text-sm font-medium leading-6 text-white">Identifiant</label>
                <div class="mt-2">
                    <input id="email" name="_username" value="{{ last_username }}" type="text" autocomplete="email" required class="block w-full rounded-md border-0 bg-white/5 py-1.5 text-white shadow-sm ring-1 ring-inset ring-white/10 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-inset focus:ring-teal-500 sm:text-sm sm:leading-6">
                </div>
            </div>

            <div>
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                    <label for="password" class="block text-sm font-medium leading-6 text-white">Mot de passe</label>
                    <div class="text-sm">
                        <a href="#" class="font-semibold text-teal-400 hover:text-teal-300">Mot de passe oublié ?</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="mt-2">
                    <input id="password" name="_password" type="password" autocomplete="current-password" required class="block w-full rounded-md border-0 bg-white/5 py-1.5 text-white shadow-sm ring-1 ring-inset ring-white/10 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-inset focus:ring-teal-500 sm:text-sm sm:leading-6">
                </div>
            </div>

            <input type="hidden" name="_csrf_token" value="{{ csrf_token('authenticate') }}">

            <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                <div class="flex items-center">
                    <input id="remember-me" name="_remember_me" checked type="checkbox" class="h-4 w-4 rounded border-gray-300 text-teal-600 focus:ring-teal-600">
                    <label for="remember-me" class="ml-3 block text-sm leading-6 text-white">Se souvenir de moi</label>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div>
                <button type="submit" class="flex w-full justify-center rounded-md bg-teal-500 px-3 py-1.5 text-sm font-semibold leading-6 text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-teal-400 focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-teal-500">Se connecter</button>
            </div>
        </form>

    </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>

{% extends 'game/base.html.twig' %}

{% block content %}

    <div id="mainWrapper">

        <div class="clouds"></div>

        <div class="content">

            <section>

                <h1>Inscription</h1>

                <form method="post" action="{{ remote ? path('game_remote_signup') : path('game_signup') }}">

                    <input type="hidden" name="_csrf_token" value="{{ csrf_token('authenticate') }}">

                    <p>
                        <label>Email</label>
                        <input id="email" name="_username" value="{{ last_username }}" type="text" autocomplete="email" required>
                    </p>

                    <p>
                        <label>Mot de passe</label>
                        <input type="text" name="name[]" value="{{ form.name is defined ? form.name[1] }}" required>
                    </p>

                    <p>
                        <label>Mail</label>
                        <input type="email" name="email" value="{{ form.email is defined ? form.email }}" required>
                        {% if errors.email is defined %} <span class="error">Cette adresse mail est déjà utilisée.</span> {% endif %}
                    </p>

                    <p><label>Numéro de portable</label><input type="tel" name="data[tel]"  value="{{ form.data is defined ? form.data.tel }}" required>
                        {% if errors.tel is defined %} <span class="error">Ce numéro de téléphone est déjà utilisé.</span> {% endif %}
                    </p>

                    <p><label>Ville</label><input type="text" name="data[ville]"  value="{{ form.data is defined ? form.data.ville }}" required></p>


                    <p>
                        Nous collectons ces données afin de gérer votre inscription au tirage au sort. En cas de victoire,
                        vous serez averti par email et par SMS. En savoir plus sur la gestion de vos données et vos droits
                        <a href="{{ asset('reglement2022.pdf') }}" target="_blank">ici</a>.
                    </p>


                    <p>Nous collectons des données pour permettre
                        à ROUEN-EXPO EVENEMENTS et ses partenaires (<a href="{{ asset('reglement2022.pdf') }}" target="_blank">voir la liste</a>) de vous
                        adresser des publicités. Pour le permettre, cochez les cases ci-dessous :</p>

                    <p><input type="checkbox"
                              id="form_auth_sms_pub"
                              name="data[authSmsPub]"
                                {{ form.data is defined and form.data.authSmsPub is defined and form.data.authSmsPub ? 'checked'}}>
                        J'accepte de recevoir par SMS des offres promotionnelles de la part de ROUEN-EXPO EVENEMENTS et ses partenaires.</p>

                    <p>
                        <input type="checkbox"
                               id="form_auth_mail_pub"
                               name="data[authMailPub]"
                                {{ form.data is defined and form.data.authMailPub is defined and form.data.authMailPub ? 'checked'}}>
                        J'accepte de recevoir par email des offres promotionnelles de la part de ROUEN-EXPO EVENEMENTS et ses partenaires.
                    </p>


                    <p class="mtm"><input type="checkbox" name="gcu" required> J'accepte le <a href="{{ asset('reglement2022.pdf') }}" target="_blank">règlement</a></p>

                    <p class="mtm"><button class="button redButton blockButton">Valider</button></p>

                </form>

            </section>

        </div>
    </div>

{% endblock content %}
